## Version 0.1.0
---

Release highlights:

* Made the running processes update instantly upon purging them.
* Provided keyboard short cuts for all batch tasks such as starting and stopping all.
* Added ability to provide extra command line arguments to `dotnet run`

---

## Keyboard Shortcuts

All batch tasks now have keyboard shortcuts making them easier to execute.

![Batch Tasks Shortcuts](data:image/png;base64,)

## Command line Arguments

When configuring an application extra arguments can be provided. These are a space delimited list of arguments that will be provided along with the dotnet run command *after* all other arguments.

This could be useful if for example an MVC app is hosting an Angular App and you want to toggle live reloading based on a command line flag.

![Command line arguments](data:image/png;base64,)
---

## Technical Notes

* Classes for web worker hosts and children have been created. These allow easy message-based communication between the two.
* Dropdown web component implemented.
